Global Pet Diets Market Insights
Pet Diets Market size was valued at USD 36.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 55.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Pet Diets Market Overview
The global pet diets market size was valued at approximately USD 21.3 billion in 2023 and is expected to reach USD 31.8 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.9% from 2024 to 2030. This growth can be attributed to rising pet ownership, increasing awareness of pet health, and the growing trend of premium pet foods. The market is experiencing robust expansion due to a shift towards natural, organic, and sustainable pet food options. Increasing disposable income and urbanization also contribute significantly to market growth, particularly in emerging economies.

